description.narrative: The overall objective of the project is to improve the health status of the rural and semi-rural population of Kenya. The specific objective of the project is to assist the Government of Kenya to implement its Development Plan (1984-88) which emphasized the development of rural and district health facilities and on strengthening their managerial capabilities.
